  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoSuggestion<T>
    The AutoSuggestion program implements an application that handles the property of autosuggestion while searching.
    ConfirmController
    This class controls the confirmation page.
    CustomCell
    The CustomCell program implements an application that sets text and tooltip to the cells of the table.
    DetailsController
    The DetailsController program implements an application that parses a html file and appends the details of a searched function to a webview.
    DispInfo
    The DispInfo program implements an application that creates a variable type which contains different variables.
    DisplayFunctions
    The DisplayFunctions program implements an application that searches the information by a header name, extracts function name, parameters and return type from the formateed string and appends those to the text area.
    DisplayHeader
    The DisplayHeader program implements an application that searches the information by a function name, extracts header name, parameters and return type of the function from the formateed string, appends those to the text area and prepares a link for getting details.
    GenerateFunctionList
    The GenerateFunctionList program implements an application that generates the list of every functions and by this time also maps informations got from calling parse method from ParseForDispHead calss.
    GenerateHeaderList
    The GenerateHeaderList program implements an application that generates the full header files(which has at leat one function) list.
    HomePageController
    This class controls everything of home page.
    Main
    The Main class shows the home page and the application starts from this.
    ParseForDispFun
    The ParseForDispFun program implements an application that parses a string in the format - 'function_name'('parameters')\n Returns - 'return_type'.
    ParseForDispHead
    The ParseForDispHead program implements an application that parses a string in the format - 'function_name'Parameters : 'parameters'\n\nReturns : 'return_type'.
    SearchSecondaryHeader
    The SearchSecondaryHeader program implements an application that checks whether a secondary header for a function exists or not.
